  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-04 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level 3. Seven factors are assessed; two factors (Model inputs and Equivalency of input parameters) are flagged as not-assessed on grounds that characterisation work is 'beyond the current project scope', without concrete justification for deferral. This constitutes the W-EP-04 weakness: unassessed factors at an elevated model risk level materially weaken overall credibility while the package decision records Accepted.",
