    "rationale": "Seven of thirteen credibility factors have been assessed; the majority of assessed factors meet or approach required levels for Model Risk Level 3. Three factors (Use error, Model inputs, Equivalency of input parameters) remain not-assessed, attributed to project scope constraints. The team judges the assessed evidence sufficient to accept the package for submission, noting that unassessed factors will be addressed in a subsequent assessment cycle. Decision: Accepted.",
